---
title: Creamy Chive Chicken with Lemony Rice & Roasted Broccoli
description: We’re big fans of pan sauces because they’re an easy way to add tons of restaurant-level flair to your dish. Here, tangy lemon juice, punchy Dijon, sour cream, and fresh chives mingle to create a condiment that takes seared chicken to the next level. On the side, there’s zesty lemon rice and roasted broccoli—because you only deserve the best!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/creamy-chive-chicken-cc54460d.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/creamy-chive-chicken-6113d3688a447f293b15f7b2-6113e789.pdf
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/creamy-chive-chicken-6113d3688a447f293b15f7b2
servings: 2
time required: 30 minutes
author: HelloFresh
course: main course
cuisine: North America
